"mogoče urejati samo prek aplikacije Nadzorne plošče "
"<build_and_customize_dashboards/customize>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:203
msgid ""
"A newly created dashboard is by default accessible to users belonging to the "
