msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Naloži predlogo`: Izberite vnaprej nastavljeno predlogo in "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Naloži predlogo`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/knowledge.rst:36
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Build an Item Kanban`: Create items to visualize and manage them "
"in a Kanban view."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Zgradite Kanban postavk`: Ustvarite postavke za njihovo "
"vizualizacijo in upravljanje v pogledu Kanban."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/knowledge.rst:37
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Build an Item List`: Create a structured list of items to "
