#: ../../content/applications/productivity/knowledge.rst:300
msgid ":guilabel:`Members`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/knowledge.rst:301
msgid ""
"The article is only visible in the sidebar tree to :ref:`invited users "
"<knowledge/articles_editing/invite>`, while other users can find it using "
"the hidden article search by pressing `CTRL` / `CMD` + `K` and typing `$`."
