msgid ""
"In Argentina, electronic signatures are regulated under the `Digital "
"Signature Law <https://www.argentina.gob.ar/normativa/nacional/70749/"
"actualizacion>`_, and the `Civil and Commercial Code <https://www.wipo.int/"
"wipolex/en/legislation/details/19085>`_. The law governs transactions "
"performed through electronic means and the use of electronic signatures. The "
"key points of the law include:"
msgstr ""
