"legislation/details/19085>`_. Zakon ureja transakcije, opravljene z "
"elektronskimi sredstvi, in uporabo elektronskih podpisov. Ključne točke "
"zakona vključujejo:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign/argentina.rst:23
msgid ""
"**Qualified digital signatures**: the law recognizes electronic signatures "
"supported by digital certificates issued by accredited Certification Service "
"Providers."
msgstr ""
"**Kvalificirani digitalni podpisi**: zakon priznava elektronske podpise, "
"podprte z digitalnimi certifikati, ki jih izdajajo akreditirani ponudniki "
