"template, you need to :ref:`edit the template <spreadsheet/get-started/"
"templates-manage>`."
msgstr ""
"Ko je preglednica shranjena kot predloga, se vse nadaljnje spremembe odprte "
"preglednice shranijo samo v tej preglednici. Če želite spremeniti predlogo, "
"morate :ref:`urediti predlogo <spreadsheet/get-started/templates-manage>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/get_started.rst:72
msgid ""
"You can also create a template by :ref:`making a copy of an existing "
"template and editing it <spreadsheet/get-started/templates-manage>`."
msgstr ""
"Predlogo lahko ustvarite tudi tako, da :ref:`naredite kopijo obstoječe "
"predloge in jo uredite <spreadsheet/get-started/templates-manage>`."

