msgstr "Agenti se lahko pridružijo klicni vrsti na tri načine:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:57
msgid "Static agents connect automatically."
msgstr "Statični agenti se povežejo samodejno."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:59
msgid "Static agents are always signed into the call queue."
msgstr "Statični agenti so vedno prijavljeni v klicno vrsto."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:61
msgid ""
"Manager logs in specific agents, via the `Axivox management console <https://"
"manage.axivox.com>`_."
msgstr ""
"Vodja prijavi določene agente prek `konzole za upravljanje Axivox <https://"
"manage.axivox.com>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:62
msgid "Agent connects to the queue in Odoo, via the **VoIP** widget."
msgstr "Agent se poveže v vrsto v Odooju prek gradnika **VoIP**."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:65
msgid "Connect to the queue through Axivox"
msgstr "Povežite se v vrsto prek Axivox"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:67
msgid ""
"Once the call queue is set up and the changes are applied, a manager can log "
"into the `Axivox management console <https://manage.axivox.com>`_ and "
"connect dynamic agents to the queue manually."
msgstr ""
"Ko je klicna vrsta nastavljena in so spremembe uveljavljene, se lahko vodja "
"prijavi v `konzolo za upravljanje Axivox <https://manage.axivox.com>`_ in "
"ročno poveže dinamične agente v vrsto."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:70
msgid ""
"To connect an agent, click :guilabel:`Queues`, located in the left-hand "
"menu. Doing so opens the :guilabel:`Queues` dashboard, with a few different "
"columns listed:"
msgstr ""
"Za povezavo agenta kliknite :guilabel:`Queues` v levem meniju. S tem se "
"odpre nadzorna plošča :guilabel:`Queues` z več stolpci:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:73
msgid ":guilabel:`Name`: name of the queue."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Name`: ime vrste."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:74
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Extension`: number of the extension to be dialed to reach the "
"queue."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Extension`: številka interne linije, ki jo je treba poklicati za "
"dostop do vrste."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:75
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Agent Connection`: number to dial for dynamic agents to log into "
"the queue."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Agent Connection`: številka, ki jo pokličejo dinamični agenti za "
"prijavo v vrsto."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:76
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Agent disconnection`: number to dial for dynamic agents to log "
"out of the queue."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Agent disconnection`: številka, ki jo pokličejo dinamični agenti "
"za odjavo iz vrste."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:77
msgid ":guilabel:`Connected Agents`: name of agents connected to the queue."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Connected Agents`: imena agentov, povezanih v vrsto."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:79
msgid ""
"The following buttons are also available on the :guilabel:`Queues` dashboard:"
msgstr "Na nadzorni plošči :guilabel:`Queues` so na voljo tudi naslednji gumbi:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:81
msgid ":guilabel:`Connect an agent`: manually connect an agent to the queue."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Connect an agent`: ročna povezava agenta v vrsto."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:82
msgid ":guilabel:`Report`: run a report on the queue."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Report`: izvedi poročilo o vrsti."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:83
msgid ":guilabel:`Delete`: delete the queue."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Delete`: izbriši vrsto."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:84
msgid ":guilabel:`Edit`: make changes to the queue's settings."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Edit`: spremeni nastavitve vrste."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:86
msgid ""
"When agents are connected to the queue, or are live with a customer, they "
"are displayed under the :guilabel:`Connected Agents` column."
msgstr ""
"Ko so agenti povezani v vrsto ali v pogovoru s stranko, so prikazani v "
"stolpcu :guilabel:`Connected Agents`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:89
msgid "If they are static agents, they **always** show up as connected."
msgstr "Če so statični agenti, so **vedno** prikazani kot povezani."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:91
msgid ""
"Connect an agent by clicking the orange button labeled :guilabel:`Connect an "
"agent`. Then, select the desired agent's name from the drop-down menu, and "
"click :guilabel:`Connect`."
msgstr ""
"Povežite agenta s klikom na oranžen gumb z oznako :guilabel:`Connect an "
"agent`. Nato izberite ime želenega agenta iz spustnega menija in kliknite "
":guilabel:`Connect`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:94
msgid ""
"To manually log a dynamic agent out of a call queue, navigate to the `Axivox "
"management console <https://manage.axivox.com>`_, and "
"click :guilabel:`Queues` from the left-hand menu. Then, click the "
"green :guilabel:`Refresh` button at the top of the :guilabel:`Connected "
"agents` column. From here, click the red :guilabel:`Disconnect` button, and "
"they are immediately disconnected. This can be helpful in situations where "
"agents forget to log out at the end of the day."
msgstr ""
"Za ročno odjavo dinamičnega agenta iz čakalne vrste za klice se pomaknite na "
"`konzolo za upravljanje Axivox <https://manage.axivox.com>`_ in v levem "
"meniju kliknite :guilabel:`Queues`. Nato kliknite zelen gumb "
":guilabel:`Refresh` na vrhu stolpca :guilabel:`Connected agents`. Tu "
"kliknite rdeč gumb :guilabel:`Disconnect` in agent bo takoj odklopljen. To "
"je lahko koristno v primerih, ko agenti pozabijo odjaviti se ob koncu dneva."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:None
msgid ""
"Call queue with connected agents column highlighted and connect an agent and "
"report buttons\n"
"highlighted."
msgstr ""
"Čakalna vrsta klicev z označenim stolpcem povezanih agentov ter označenima "
"gumboma za povezavo agenta in poročilo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:105
msgid "Report"
msgstr "Poročilo"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:107
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Report` to open a :guilabel:`Queue report` page that shows "
"queue activity. This report includes who connected and when when, as well as "
"what phone calls were handled by the queue.f This information is showcased "
"on a separate :guilabel:`Queue report` page."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Report`, da odprete stran :guilabel:`Queue report`, ki "
"prikazuje aktivnost čakalne vrste. To poročilo vključuje informacije o tem, "
"kdo se je povezal in kdaj, ter kateri telefonski klici so bili obravnavani v "
"čakalni vrsti. Te informacije so prikazane na ločeni strani :guilabel:`Queue "
"report`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:111
msgid ""
"Set the report's date in the :guilabel:`Period` field. To pick a specific "
"date range, use the :guilabel:`From` and :guilabel:`to` fields. The "
"information can be organized by :guilabel:`Event type` (covered below), "
"and :guilabel:`Call ID`."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite datum poročila v polju :guilabel:`Period`. Za izbiro določenega "
"datumskega območja uporabite polji :guilabel:`From` in :guilabel:`to`. "
"Informacije lahko organizirate po :guilabel:`Event type` (obravnavano "
"spodaj) in :guilabel:`Call ID`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:115
msgid "Generate the report by clicking :guilabel:`Apply`."
msgstr "Ustvarite poročilo s klikom na :guilabel:`Apply`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:117
msgid ""
"Each report can be exported to a :abbr:`CSV (comma separated value)` file "
"for further use and analysis, via the :guilabel:`Export to CSV` button."
msgstr ""
"Vsako poročilo je mogoče izvoziti v datoteko :abbr:`CSV (comma separated "
"value)` za nadaljnjo uporabo in analizo prek gumba :guilabel:`Export to CSV`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/axivox/call_queues.rst:120
msgid ""
"When the :guilabel:`Event type` field is clicked, a drop-down menu appears "
