#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:72
msgid "Create a Meta business account"
msgstr "Ustvarite poslovni račun Meta"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:75
msgid ""
"In order to create a Meta business account, the user must have a personal "
"Facebook account that has existed for a minimum of one hour prior to setting "
"up the Facebook Business account. Trying to create the business account "
"prior to this time results in an error."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje poslovnega računa Meta mora imeti uporabnik osebni Facebook "
"račun, ki obstaja najmanj eno uro pred nastavitvijo Facebook poslovnega "
"računa. Poskus ustvarjanja poslovnega računa pred tem časom povzroči napako."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:79
msgid ""
"To create a business account with Meta, navigate to `Meta Business Suite "
"<https://business.facebook.com/overview>`__. Click :guilabel:`Create "
"account` and then enter the business name, the administrator's name, and a "
"work email address. Click :guilabel:`Next`, and confirm the email address in "
"the pop-up window that appears. After confirming, click :guilabel:`Done` to "
"close the window."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje poslovnega računa z Meta pojdite na `Meta Business Suite "
"<https://business.facebook.com/overview>`__. Kliknite :guilabel:`Ustvari "
"račun` in nato vnesite ime podjetja, ime skrbnika in službeni e-poštni "
"naslov. Kliknite :guilabel:`Naprej` in potrdite e-poštni naslov v pojavnem "
"oknu, ki se prikaže. Po potrditvi kliknite :guilabel:`Končano`, da zaprete "
"okno."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:85
msgid ""
"Next, follow the instructions in the email sent by Facebook to confirm the "
"creation of the business account and to complete the setup process."
msgstr ""
"Nato sledite navodilom v e-poštnem sporočilu, ki ga pošlje Facebook, da "
"potrdite ustvarjanje poslovnega računa in dokončate postopek nastavitve."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:89
msgid ""
"`Set up a Meta business account <https://www.facebook.com/business/help/"
"1710077379203657?id=180505742745347>`__"
msgstr ""
"`Nastavite poslovni račun Meta <https://www.facebook.com/business/help/"
"1710077379203657?id=180505742745347>`__"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:93
msgid ""
"If the business account is linked to a personal Facebook account, the "
"administrator must switch between their personal account and the business "
"account for the remainder of the configuration."
msgstr ""
"Če je poslovni račun povezan z osebnim Facebook računom, mora skrbnik za "
"preostanek konfiguracije preklapljati med svojim osebnim računom in "
"poslovnim računom."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:96
msgid ""
"To switch to the business account, navigate to the `Meta Developer Dashboard "
"<https://developers.facebook.com>`__ and click the *account name* in the top-"
"right corner. Under :guilabel:`Business Accounts`, select the business to be "
"configured."
msgstr ""
"Za preklop na poslovni račun pojdite na `Meta Developer Dashboard <https://"
"developers.facebook.com>`__ in kliknite *ime računa* v zgornjem desnem kotu. "
"Pod :guilabel:`Poslovni računi` izberite podjetje, ki ga želite "
"konfigurirati."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:0
msgid "Toggle between Meta personal and business accounts."
msgstr "Preklop med osebnim in poslovnim računom Meta."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:106
msgid "Create a Meta developer app for Odoo"
msgstr "Ustvarite Meta razvijalsko aplikacijo za Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:108
msgid ""
"On the `Meta Developer Dashboard <https://developers.facebook.com>`__ "
"dashboard, sign in with the Meta developer account. If no account is "
"configured yet, link a Facebook account to create a Meta developer account."
msgstr ""
"Na nadzorni plošči `Meta Developer Dashboard <https://"
"developers.facebook.com>`__ se prijavite z Meta razvijalskim računom. Če "
"račun še ni konfiguriran, povežite Facebook račun, da ustvarite Meta "
"razvijalski račun."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:113
msgid ""
"A Facebook *developer* account is different than a Facebook *business* "
"account. While developer accounts are tied to personal Facebook accounts, "
"business accounts are **not** as they represent a business and manage all of "
"the business's assets in Meta, such as apps."
msgstr ""
"Facebook *razvijalski* račun se razlikuje od Facebook *poslovnega* računa. "
"Medtem ko so razvijalski računi povezani z osebnimi Facebook računi, "
"poslovni računi **niso**, saj predstavljajo podjetje in upravljajo vse "
"poslovne vire v Meta, kot so aplikacije."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:118
msgid ""
"`Set up the WhatsApp Business Platform <https://www.facebookblueprint.com/"
"student/collection/409587/path/360218>`__"
msgstr ""
"`Nastavite WhatsApp Business Platform <https://www.facebookblueprint.com/"
"student/collection/409587/path/360218>`__"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:121
msgid ""
"After signing in to the Meta developer account, click :guilabel:`My Apps` in "
"the top-right corner. This redirects the administrator to all the apps the "
"developer has configured in the specific developer account. "
"Click :guilabel:`Create App` to configure a new Meta application."
msgstr ""
"Po prijavi v Meta razvijalski račun kliknite :guilabel:`Moje aplikacije` v "
"zgornjem desnem kotu. To preusmeri skrbnika na vse aplikacije, ki jih je "
"razvijalec konfiguriral v določenem razvijalskem računu. Kliknite "
":guilabel:`Ustvari aplikacijo`, da konfigurirate novo Meta aplikacijo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:128
msgid "Add app details"
msgstr "Dodajte podrobnosti aplikacije"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:130
msgid ""
"The first step of the :guilabel:`Create an app` process is to fill out "
"the :guilabel:`App details` section. Enter `Odoo` in the :guilabel:`App "
"name` field."
msgstr ""
"Prvi korak postopka :guilabel:`Ustvari aplikacijo` je izpolnitev razdelka "
":guilabel:`Podrobnosti aplikacije`. V polje :guilabel:`Ime aplikacije` "
"vnesite `Odoo`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:134
msgid "The app name can be changed in the settings afterward."
msgstr "Ime aplikacije lahko pozneje spremenite v nastavitvah."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:137
msgid ""
"Trademarks and branded elements may **not** be used in this text section. "
"This includes the Meta group of companies. Do **not** include the word "
"`WhatsApp` or the system flags this as an error."
msgstr ""
"Blagovnih znamk in znamčenih elementov **ne smete** uporabljati v tem "
"besedilnem razdelku. To vključuje skupino podjetij Meta. **Ne** vključujte "
"besede `WhatsApp`, sicer sistem to označi kot napako."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:140
msgid ""
"Next, enter the developer email address in the :guilabel:`App contact email` "
"field, then click :guilabel:`Next`."
msgstr ""
"Nato vnesite e-poštni naslov razvijalca v polje :guilabel:`Kontaktni e-"
"poštni naslov aplikacije`, nato kliknite :guilabel:`Naprej`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:146
msgid "Select the app type"
msgstr "Izberite vrsto aplikacije"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:148
msgid ""
"The next step in app creation is the ::guilabel:`Use cases` section. "
"Under :menuselection:`Filter by`, select :guilabel:`Others`, "
"select :guilabel:`Others`, then click :guilabel:`Next`. The page redirects "
"to :guilabel:`Select an app type`."
msgstr ""
"Naslednji korak pri ustvarjanju aplikacije je razdelek ::guilabel:`Primeri "
"uporabe`. Pod :menuselection:`Filtriraj po` izberite :guilabel:`Drugo`, "
"izberite :guilabel:`Drugo`, nato kliknite :guilabel:`Naprej`. Stran vas "
"preusmeri na :guilabel:`Izberite vrsto aplikacije`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:152
msgid ""
"Select :guilabel:`Business`. This selection allows for the creation and "
"management of the WhatsApp :abbr:`API (Application Programming Interface)`. "
"Click :guilabel:`Next` to configure the app as desired."
msgstr ""
"Izberite :guilabel:`Poslovna`. Ta izbira omogoča ustvarjanje in upravljanje "
"WhatsApp :abbr:`API (vmesnika za programiranje aplikacij)`. Kliknite "
":guilabel:`Naprej`, da konfigurirate aplikacijo po želji."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:159
msgid "Select the business portfolio"
msgstr "Izberi poslovno zbirko"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:161
msgid ""
"The last step of the app creation process is to connect a business portfolio."
msgstr ""
"Zadnji korak postopka ustvarjanja aplikacije je povezava poslovne zbirke."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:163
msgid ""
"Under :guilabel:`Business portfolio - Optional`, click the drop-down menu "
"and select the Meta business account profile. Review the *Meta Platform "
"Terms* and *Developer Policies* agreements, then click :guilabel:`Create "
"app` to accept and create the app."
msgstr ""
"V razdelku :guilabel:`Poslovna zbirka - neobvezno` kliknite spustni meni in "
"izberite profil poslovnega računa Meta. Preglejte pogodbi *Meta Platform "
"Terms* in *Developer Policies*, nato kliknite :guilabel:`Ustvari "
"aplikacijo`, da sprejmete in ustvarite aplikacijo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:167
msgid ""
"To accept the agreements and create the app, enter the Facebook account "
"password and click :guilabel:`Submit`. The browser then redirects to "
"the :guilabel:`Meta for Developers` dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Če želite sprejeti pogodbe in ustvariti aplikacijo, vnesite geslo računa "
"Facebook in kliknite :guilabel:`Pošlji`. Brskalnik nato preusmeri na "
"nadzorno ploščo :guilabel:`Meta for Developers`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:171
msgid ""
"If the Meta business account is prohibited from advertising, the app cannot "
"be claimed. To resolve this issue, navigate to `Meta Business Suite <https://"
"business.facebook.com/business>`__ for assistance."
msgstr ""
"Če je poslovnemu računu Meta prepovedano oglaševanje, aplikacije ni mogoče "
"zahtevati. Za rešitev te težave pojdite na `Meta Business Suite <https://"
"business.facebook.com/business>`__ za pomoč."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:175
msgid ""
"For more information, see `Meta's documentation on advertising restrictions "
"<https://www.facebook.com/business/help/975570072950669>`_."
msgstr ""
"Za več informacij glejte `dokumentacijo Meta o omejitvah oglaševanja "
"<https://www.facebook.com/business/help/975570072950669>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:181
msgid "Add a WhatsApp product to the app"
msgstr "Dodajte izdelek WhatsApp v aplikacijo"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:183
msgid ""
"Now that the basic structure of the app has been created, a product needs to "
"be added to the app. Navigate to the `Meta Developer Dashboard <https://"
"developers.facebook.com/apps>`__, and click on the app that is being "
"configured. The page redirects to the app's dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj, ko je osnovna struktura aplikacije ustvarjena, je treba aplikaciji "
"dodati izdelek. Pojdite na `Nadzorno ploščo Meta Developer <https://"
"developers.facebook.com/apps>`__ in kliknite aplikacijo, ki jo nastavljate. "
"Stran preusmeri na nadzorno ploščo aplikacije."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:187
msgid ""
"Under :guilabel:`Add products to your app`, go to WhatsApp near the bottom "
"of the page and click :guilabel:`Set up`."
msgstr ""
"V razdelku :guilabel:`Dodaj izdelke svoji aplikaciji` pojdite na WhatsApp "
"blizu dna strani in kliknite :guilabel:`Nastavi`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:191
msgid ""
"`Meta's WhatsApp developer documentation <https://developers.facebook.com/"
"docs/whatsapp/>`__"
msgstr ""
"`Razvijalska dokumentacija Meta za WhatsApp <https://developers.facebook.com/"
"docs/whatsapp/>`__"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:193
msgid ""
"The browser then redirects to the configuration page for "
"the :guilabel:`WhatsApp Business Platform API`."
msgstr ""
"Brskalnik nato preusmeri na stran za konfiguracijo :guilabel:`WhatsApp "
"Business Platform API`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:196
msgid ""
"Under :guilabel:`Select a Meta Business Account` option, select the Meta "
"business to be configured, then click :guilabel:`Continue` to confirm the "
"selection and agree to Meta's terms and conditions as linked on "
"the :guilabel:`Meta App Dashboard`."
msgstr ""
"V možnosti :guilabel:`Izberi Meta Business Account` izberite podjetje Meta, "
"ki ga želite konfigurirati, nato kliknite :guilabel:`Nadaljuj`, da potrdite "
"izbiro in sprejmete Metine pogoje poslovanja, kot so povezani na "
":guilabel:`Nadzorni plošči aplikacije Meta`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:200
msgid ""
"Once the WhatsApp product is added to the app, Meta provides a WhatsApp test "
"phone number. This test phone number can send unlimited messages to a "
"maximum of five recipients."
msgstr ""
"Ko je izdelek WhatsApp dodan aplikaciji, Meta zagotovi testno telefonsko "
"številko WhatsApp. Ta testna telefonska številka lahko pošlje neomejeno "
"število sporočil največ petim prejemnikom."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:203
msgid ""
"Under :guilabel:`Send and receive messages`, select the :guilabel:`To` field "
"and choose :guilabel:`Manage phone number list`. Add up to five valid "
"WhatsApp number as recipients, then enter the confirmation codes sent to "
"those phone numbers in WhatsApp to verify."
msgstr ""
"V razdelku :guilabel:`Pošlji in prejmi sporočila` izberite polje "
":guilabel:`Za` in izberite :guilabel:`Upravljaj seznam telefonskih številk`. "
"Dodajte do pet veljavnih številk WhatsApp kot prejemnike, nato vnesite "
"potrditvene kode, poslane na te telefonske številke v WhatsApp, da jih "
"preverite."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:208
msgid ""
"`WhatsApp Cloud API guide <https://developers.facebook.com/docs/whatsapp/"
"cloud-api/get-started#add-recipient-number>`__"
msgstr ""
"`Vodnik po oblačnem API-ju WhatsApp <https://developers.facebook.com/docs/"
"whatsapp/cloud-api/get-started#add-recipient-number>`__"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:214
msgid "WhatsApp API quickstart"
msgstr "Hitri začetek API-ja WhatsApp"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:216
msgid ""
"Once the Meta accounts and app have been configured, "
"click :guilabel:`Continue` to proceed to the WhatsApp :guilabel:`Quickstart` "
"page. This page provides a starting point for configuring the WhatsApp API "
"by adding a phone number and sending an initial test message."
msgstr ""
"Ko so računi Meta in aplikacija konfigurirani, kliknite "
":guilabel:`Nadaljuj`, da nadaljujete na stran :guilabel:`Hitri začetek` za "
"WhatsApp. Ta stran zagotavlja izhodišče za konfiguracijo API-ja WhatsApp z "
"dodajanjem telefonske številke in pošiljanjem začetnega testnega sporočila."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:221
msgid ""
"If the browser does not automatically redirect to the "
"WhatsApp :guilabel:`Quickstart` page, navigate to the `Meta Developer "
"Dashboard <https://developers.facebook.com/apps>`__ and select the `Odoo` "
"app."
msgstr ""
"Če brskalnik ne preusmeri samodejno na stran WhatsApp :guilabel:`Hiter "
"začetek`, pojdite na `Nadzorno ploščo Meta Developer <https://"
"developers.facebook.com/apps>`__ in izberite aplikacijo `Odoo`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:225
msgid ""
"In the menu on the left-hand side of the page, click the :icon:`fa-chevron-"
"down` :guilabel:`(down chevron)` icon next to the :guilabel:`WhatsApp` "
"section heading. A small menu opens, containing the following options:"
msgstr ""
"V meniju na levi strani strani kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-chevron-down` "
":guilabel:`(puščica navzdol)` poleg naslova razdelka :guilabel:`WhatsApp`. "
"Odpre se majhen meni z naslednjimi možnostmi:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:229
msgid ":guilabel:`Quickstart`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Hiter začetek`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:230
msgid ":guilabel:`API setup`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Nastavitev API`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:231
msgid ":guilabel:`Configuration`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Konfiguracija`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:233
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Quickstart` option, and then click :guilabel:`Start "
"using the API`."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite možnost :guilabel:`Hiter začetek` in nato kliknite "
":guilabel:`Začnite uporabljati API`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:238
msgid "API setup"
msgstr "Nastavitev API"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:240
msgid ""
"After clicking on :guilabel:`Start using the API`, the page navigates to "
"the :guilabel:`API setup`. Now that the test number has been created, a test "
"message can be sent to confirm that WhatsApp is working properly. Navigate "
"to the :guilabel:`Send and receive messages` section. Under :guilabel:`Step "
"1 Select phone numbers`, click the drop-down menu next to :guilabel:`To`."
msgstr ""
"Po kliku na :guilabel:`Začni uporabljati API` se stran preusmeri na "
":guilabel:`Nastavitev API`. Zdaj, ko je testna številka ustvarjena, lahko "
"pošljete testno sporočilo za potrditev, da WhatsApp deluje pravilno. Pojdite "
"na razdelek :guilabel:`Pošiljanje in prejemanje sporočil`. Pod "
":guilabel:`Korak 1 Izbira telefonskih številk` kliknite spustni meni poleg "
":guilabel:`Za`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:245
msgid ""
"Next, select the only option available: :guilabel:`Manage phone number "
"list`. Follow the steps and add up to five phone numbers to send the free "
"test messages to. Enter the appropriate country code and phone number, then "
"click :guilabel:`Next`."
msgstr ""
"Nato izberite edino razpoložljivo možnost: :guilabel:`Upravljaj seznam "
"telefonskih številk`. Sledite korakom in dodajte do pet telefonskih številk, "
"na katere boste poslali brezplačna testna sporočila. Vnesite ustrezno kodo "
"države in telefonsko številko, nato kliknite :guilabel:`Naprej`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:250
msgid ""
"Adding a phone number to send to in this step allows for a successful test "
"to be sent by the terminal. This is critical to ensure the "
"WhatsApp :abbr:`API (Application Programming Interface)` is working."
msgstr ""
"Dodajanje telefonske številke za pošiljanje v tem koraku omogoča uspešno "
"pošiljanje testnega sporočila prek terminala. To je ključno za zagotovitev, "
"da :abbr:`API (vmesnik za programiranje aplikacij)` za WhatsApp deluje."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:254
msgid ""
"On the next page, enter the verification code sent to the phone numbers, and "
"click :guilabel:`Next` to verify the numbers."
msgstr ""
"Na naslednji strani vnesite potrditveno kodo, poslano na telefonske "
"številke, in kliknite :guilabel:`Naprej`, da preverite številke."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:260
msgid "Send a test message via terminal"
msgstr "Pošljite testno sporočilo prek terminala"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:262
msgid ""
"Once the phone number has been verified, send a test message via the "
"terminal. Under :guilabel:`Step 2 Send messages with the API`, "
"click :guilabel:`Send Message`. This should send a test message to the phone "
"numbers that were added."
msgstr ""
"Ko je telefonska številka preverjena, pošljite testno sporočilo prek "
"terminala. V razdelku :guilabel:`2. korak Pošiljanje sporočil z API-jem` "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Pošlji sporočilo`. To bi moralo poslati testno sporočilo "
"na telefonske številke, ki so bile dodane."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:266
msgid ""
"Upon successfully receiving the message to the numbers, move onto the next "
"section to :ref:`produce and configure webhooks <productivity/whatsapp/"
"webhooks>`."
msgstr ""
"Po uspešnem prejemu sporočila na številke nadaljujte na naslednji razdelek "
"za :ref:`ustvarjanje in konfiguracijo webhookov <productivity/whatsapp/"
"webhooks>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:272
msgid "WhatsApp configuration in Odoo"
msgstr "Konfiguracija WhatsApp v Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:274
msgid ""
"To create a :guilabel:`Callback URL` and :guilabel:`Webhook Verify Token`, "
"the phone number, token, app ID, and account ID need to be configured in "
"Odoo; these values are used to set up webhooks, which make it possible to "
"receive messages in the database. The configuration steps in this section "
"are all performed in the Odoo database."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje :guilabel:`URL-ja za povratni klic` in :guilabel:`žetona za "
"preverjanje webhooka` je treba v Odoo konfigurirati telefonsko številko, "
"žeton, ID aplikacije in ID računa; te vrednosti se uporabijo za nastavitev "
"webhookov, ki omogočajo prejemanje sporočil v bazi podatkov. Vsi koraki "
"konfiguracije v tem razdelku se izvajajo v bazi podatkov Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:279
msgid ""
"In Odoo, navigate to :menuselection:`WhatsApp app --> Configuration --> "
"WhatsApp Business Accounts`, then click :guilabel:`New` to configure the "
"WhatsApp business account in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"V Odoo pojdite na :menuselection:`WhatsApp aplikacija --> Konfiguracija --> "
"Poslovni računi WhatsApp`, nato kliknite :guilabel:`Novo`, da konfigurirate "
"poslovni račun WhatsApp v Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:282
msgid ""
"In another browser tab, navigate to `Meta Developer Dashboard <https://"
"developers.facebook.com>`__. Select :menuselection:`My Apps --> WhatsApp --> "
"API Configuration`, and then copy the following values from the Meta "
"developer console into the corresponding fields in Odoo:"
msgstr ""
"V drugem zavihku brskalnika pojdite na `Nadzorno ploščo za razvijalce Meta "
"<https://developers.facebook.com>`__. Izberite :menuselection:`Moje "
"aplikacije --> WhatsApp --> Konfiguracija API-ja`, nato pa kopirajte "
"naslednje vrednosti iz konzole za razvijalce Meta v ustrezna polja v Odoo:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:291
msgid "Meta Console"
msgstr "Meta konzola"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:292
msgid "Odoo Interface"
msgstr "Vmesnik Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:293
msgid "Phone"
msgstr "Telefon"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:294
msgid ":guilabel:`Phone number ID`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`ID telefonske številke`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:295
msgid ":guilabel:`Phone Number ID`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`ID telefonske številke`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:296
msgid "Token"
msgstr "Žeton"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:297
msgid ":guilabel:`Temporary access token`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Začasni žeton za dostop`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:298
msgid ":guilabel:`Access Token`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Žeton za dostop`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:299
msgid "App ID"
msgstr "ID aplikacije"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:300
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:301
msgid ":guilabel:`App ID`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`ID aplikacije`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:302
msgid "Account ID"
msgstr "ID računa"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:303
msgid ":guilabel:`WhatsApp Business Account ID`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`ID računa WhatsApp Business`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:304
msgid ":guilabel:`Account ID`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`ID računa`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:306
msgid ""
"To retrieve the :guilabel:`App Secret`, navigate to the `Meta Developer "
"Dashboard <https://developers.facebook.com/apps>`__, and select the `Odoo` "
"app. In the left-hand side menu, under :guilabel:`App settings`, "
"select :guilabel:`Basic`."
msgstr ""
"Za pridobitev :guilabel:`skrivnosti aplikacije` pojdite na `Nadzorno ploščo "
"za razvijalce Meta <https://developers.facebook.com/apps>`__ in izberite "
"aplikacijo `Odoo`. V levem meniju pod :guilabel:`Nastavitve aplikacije` "
"izberite :guilabel:`Osnovno`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:310
msgid ""
"Next, click :guilabel:`Show` next to :guilabel:`App secret`, and enter the "
"account password. Copy the :guilabel:`App secret` and then paste it into "
"the :guilabel:`App Secret` field on the Odoo :guilabel:`WhatsApp Business "
"Account` configuration dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Nato kliknite :guilabel:`Prikaži` poleg :guilabel:`Skrivnost aplikacije` in "
"vnesite geslo računa. Kopirajte :guilabel:`skrivnost aplikacije` in jo "
"prilepite v polje :guilabel:`Skrivnost aplikacije` na nadzorni plošči "
"konfiguracije :guilabel:`poslovnega računa WhatsApp` v Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:314
msgid ""
"To complete the setup of the WhatsApp business account in Odoo, "
"click :guilabel:`Test Connection`. If the configuration is set correctly, a "
"successful message in green populates the upper-right corner of the "
"dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Za dokončanje nastavitve poslovnega računa WhatsApp v Odoo kliknite "
":guilabel:`Preveri povezavo`. Če je konfiguracija pravilna, se v zgornjem "
"desnem kotu nadzorne plošče prikaže zeleno sporočilo o uspehu."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:321
msgid "Configure webhooks"
msgstr "Konfiguracija webhookov"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:323
msgid ""
"To configure the webhooks for the Odoo **WhatsApp** app, navigate to the "
"`Meta Developer Dashboard <https://developers.facebook.com/apps>`__, and "
"select the `Odoo` app. In the left-hand side menu, "
"click :menuselection:`WhatsApp --> API setup`. Go to :guilabel:`Step 3: "
"Configure webhooks to receive messages` and click :guilabel:`Configure "
"webhooks`."
msgstr ""
"Za konfiguracijo webhookov za Odoo aplikacijo **WhatsApp** pojdite na "
"`Nadzorno ploščo Meta Developer <https://developers.facebook.com/apps>`__ in "
"izberite aplikacijo `Odoo`. V meniju na levi strani kliknite "
":menuselection:`WhatsApp --> Nastavitev API`. Pojdite na :guilabel:`Korak 3: "
"Konfiguriraj webhooke za prejemanje sporočil` in kliknite "
":guilabel:`Konfiguriraj webhooke`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:329
msgid ""
"Webhook configuration settings can also be accessed by navigating to the "
"`Meta Developer Dashboard <https://developers.facebook.com/apps>`__, "
"selecting the `Odoo` app, and then selecting :guilabel:`Webhooks` in the "
"left hand menu."
msgstr ""
"Do nastavitev konfiguracije webhookov lahko dostopate tudi tako, da obiščete "
"`Nadzorno ploščo za razvijalce Meta <https://developers.facebook.com/apps>"
"`__, izberete aplikacijo `Odoo` in nato v levem meniju izberete "
":guilabel:`Webhooki`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:0
msgid "Manually navigating to the WhatsApp webhooks configuration."
msgstr "Ročno navigiranje do konfiguracije WhatsApp webhookov."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:336
msgid ""
"On the :menuselection:`Webhook configuration` page, click :guilabel:`Edit`. "
"This is where the :guilabel:`Callback URL` and :guilabel:`Webhook Verify "
"Token` values from Odoo are added."
msgstr ""
"Na strani :menuselection:`Konfiguracija webhooka` kliknite "
":guilabel:`Uredi`. Tu se dodajo vrednosti :guilabel:`URL-ja za povratni "
"klic` in :guilabel:`žetona za preverjanje webhooka` iz Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:340
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Callback URL` and :guilabel:`Webhook Verify Token` values are "
"both automatically populated after clicking on :guilabel:`Test Connection` "
"in the previous step."
msgstr ""
"Vrednosti :guilabel:`URL-ja za povratni klic` in :guilabel:`žetona za "
"preverjanje webhooka` se samodejno zapolnijo po kliku na :guilabel:`Preveri "
"povezavo` v prejšnjem koraku."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:343
msgid ""
"In a separate browser window, retrieve the necessary values in Odoo by "
"navigating to :menuselection:`WhatsApp app --> Configuration --> WhatsApp "
"Business Accounts` and then selecting the account that is being configured. "
"The values are located under :guilabel:`Receiving Messages`."
msgstr ""
"V ločenem oknu brskalnika pridobite potrebne vrednosti v Odoo tako, da "
"pojdete na :menuselection:`WhatsApp aplikacija --> Konfiguracija --> "
"Poslovni računi WhatsApp` in nato izberete račun, ki ga konfigurirate. "
"Vrednosti se nahajajo pod :guilabel:`Prejemanje sporočil`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:347
msgid ""
"Copy and paste the :guilabel:`Callback URL` from Odoo into "
"the :guilabel:`Callback URL` field in Meta, then copy and paste "
"the :guilabel:`Webhook Verify Token` into the :guilabel:`Verify Token` field "
"on the Meta developer console. Click :guilabel:`Verify and save`."
msgstr ""
"Kopirajte in prilepite :guilabel:`URL za povratni klic` iz Odoo v polje "
":guilabel:`URL za povratni klic` v Meta, nato kopirajte in prilepite "
":guilabel:`žeton za preverjanje webhooka` v polje :guilabel:`Žeton za "
"preverjanje` v konzoli za razvijalce Meta. Kliknite :guilabel:`Preveri in "
"shrani`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:354
msgid "Add webhook fields"
msgstr "Dodajanje polj webhooka"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:356
msgid ""
"Now that the Odoo database and WhatsApp have been configured to communicate "
"with each other, the next step is to add webhook fields to specify the "
"information that should be sent between the two. To add individual webhook "
"fields in Meta's developer console, go to the :guilabel:`Webhook fields` "
"section and click :guilabel:`Manage`. In the pop-up window that loads, check "
"the boxes in the :guilabel:`Subscribe` column for the following *field "
"names*:"
msgstr ""
"Zdaj, ko sta baza podatkov Odoo in WhatsApp konfigurirana za medsebojno "
"komunikacijo, je naslednji korak dodajanje polj webhooka za določitev "
"informacij, ki naj se pošiljajo med njima. Za dodajanje posameznih polj "
"webhooka v konzoli za razvijalce Meta pojdite na razdelek :guilabel:`Polja "
"webhooka` in kliknite :guilabel:`Upravljaj`. V pojavnem oknu, ki se naloži, "
"označite potrditvena polja v stolpcu :guilabel:`Naroči se` za naslednja "
"*imena polj*:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:362
msgid "account_update"
msgstr "account_update"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:363
msgid "message_template_quality_update"
msgstr "message_template_quality_update"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:364
msgid "message_template_status_update"
msgstr "message_template_status_update"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:365
msgid "messages"
msgstr "messages"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:366
msgid "template_category_update"
msgstr "template_category_update"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:368
msgid "After making the selections, click :guilabel:`Done`."
msgstr "Po izbiri možnosti kliknite :guilabel:`Končano`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:370
msgid ""
"If the :guilabel:`Webhooks` configuration is successful, the buttons in "
"the :guilabel:`Subscribe` column should change from :guilabel:`Subscribe` "
"to :guilabel:`Unsubscribe`:"
msgstr ""
"Če je konfiguracija :guilabel:`webhookov` uspešna, bi se morali gumbi v "
"stolpcu :guilabel:`Naroči se` spremeniti iz :guilabel:`Naroči se` v "
":guilabel:`Odjavi naročnino`:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:None
msgid "WhatsApp webhooks set in the Meta developer console."
msgstr "Spletni kavlji WhatsApp, nastavljeni v konzoli za razvijalce Meta."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:377
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Webhook fields` only appear once the subscription is confirmed "
"using the :guilabel:`Callback URL` and :guilabel:`Webhook Verify Token`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Polja Webhook` se prikažejo šele, ko je naročnina potrjena z "
"uporabo :guilabel:`URL-ja povratnega klica` in :guilabel:`žetona za "
"preverjanje Webhooka`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:381
msgid ""
"`Meta's WhatsApp documentation on setting webhooks <https://"
"developers.facebook.com/docs/whatsapp/cloud-api/guides/set-up-webhooks>`__"
msgstr ""
"`Metina dokumentacija WhatsApp o nastavitvi webhookov <https://"
"developers.facebook.com/docs/whatsapp/cloud-api/guides/set-up-webhooks>`__"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:387
msgid "Add a phone number"
msgstr "Dodaj telefonsko številko"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:389
msgid ""
"To configure the business phone number to use for **WhatsApp** in Odoo, "
"navigate back to the `Meta Developer Dashboard <https://"
"developers.facebook.com/apps>`__ and select the `Odoo` app. "
"Under :guilabel:`WhatsApp` in the left-hand side menu, click :guilabel:`API "
"setup`. Go to :guilabel:`Step 5: Add a phone number`, and "
"click :guilabel:`Add phone number`."
msgstr ""
"Za konfiguracijo poslovne telefonske številke za uporabo v **WhatsApp** v "
"Odoo se vrnite na `Nadzorno ploščo Meta Developer <https://"
"developers.facebook.com/apps>`__ in izberite aplikacijo `Odoo`. Pod "
":guilabel:`WhatsApp` v meniju na levi strani kliknite :guilabel:`Nastavitev "
"API`. Pojdite na :guilabel:`Korak 5: Dodaj telefonsko številko` in kliknite "
":guilabel:`Dodaj telefonsko številko`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:394
msgid ""
"Enter a :guilabel:`Business name` and :guilabel:`Business website or profile "
"page`."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite :guilabel:`Ime podjetja` in :guilabel:`Spletno mesto podjetja ali "
"stran profila`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:397
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Business website or profile page` field can be a link to a "
"social media page."
msgstr ""
"Polje :guilabel:`Spletno mesto podjetja ali stran profila` je lahko povezava "
"do strani družbenega omrežja."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:399
msgid ""
"Select the country that the company does business in from "
"the :guilabel:`Country` drop-down menu; a business address is optional. "
"After adding the business location, click :guilabel:`Next`."
msgstr ""
"V spustnem meniju :guilabel:`Država` izberite državo, v kateri posluje "
"podjetje; poslovni naslov ni obvezen. Po dodajanju lokacije podjetja "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Naprej`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:402
msgid ""
"On the next page, fill out the following :guilabel:`WhatsApp Business "
"profile` details:"
msgstr ""
"Na naslednji strani izpolnite naslednje podatke za :guilabel:`profil "
"WhatsApp Business`:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:404
msgid ":guilabel:`WhatsApp Business Profile Display Name`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Prikazno ime profila WhatsApp Business`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:405
msgid ":guilabel:`Timezone`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Časovni pas`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:406
msgid ":guilabel:`Category`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Kategorija`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:407
msgid ":guilabel:`Business description` (optional)"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Opis podjetja` (neobvezno)"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:409
msgid ""
"Once these sections are complete, click :guilabel:`Next`. The page refreshes "
"and then prompts the administrator to :guilabel:`Add a phone number for "
"WhatsApp` in the respective field. Enter the business phone number to be "
"used with WhatsApp."
msgstr ""
"Ko so ti razdelki izpolnjeni, kliknite :guilabel:`Naprej`. Stran se osveži "
"in nato pozove skrbnika, naj :guilabel:`Doda telefonsko številko za "
"WhatsApp` v ustrezno polje. Vnesite poslovno telefonsko številko, ki bo "
"uporabljena z WhatsAppom."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:414
msgid ""
"`Migrate an Existing WhatsApp Number to a Business Account <https://"
"developers.facebook.com/docs/whatsapp/cloud-api/get-started/migrate-existing-"
"whatsapp- number-to-a-business-account>`__."
msgstr ""
"`Migrate an Existing WhatsApp Number to a Business Account <https://"
"developers.facebook.com/docs/whatsapp/cloud-api/get-started/migrate-existing-"
"whatsapp- number-to-a-business-account>`__."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:418
msgid ""
"Select :guilabel:`Text message` or :guilabel:`Phone call` for the phone "
"number verification method, and then click :guilabel:`Next` to proceed."
msgstr ""
"Izberite :guilabel:`Besedilno sporočilo` ali :guilabel:`Telefonski klic` za "
"način preverjanja telefonske številke in nato kliknite :guilabel:`Naprej`, "
"da nadaljujete."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:421
msgid ""
"The business phone number receives a WhatsApp code through the chosen "
"verification method. Enter the verification code into "
"the :guilabel:`Verification code` field and click :guilabel:`Next` to verify "
"the business phone number."
msgstr ""
"Poslovna telefonska številka prejme kodo WhatsApp prek izbranega načina "
"preverjanja. Vnesite kodo za preverjanje v polje :guilabel:`Koda za "
"preverjanje` in kliknite :guilabel:`Naprej`, da preverite poslovno "
"telefonsko številko."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:426
msgid ""
"A payment method **must** be added to proceed. This is part of Meta's fraud "
"detection system. In order to ensure that the account/company is real, a "
"payment method is required to proceed. See Meta's documentation on `how to "
"add a payment method in Meta Business Suite <https://www.facebook.com/"
"business/help/915454841921082?id=180505742745347>`__."
msgstr ""
"Način plačila se **mora** dodati, da lahko nadaljujete. To je del Metinega "
"sistema za odkrivanje goljufij. Da se zagotovi, da je račun/podjetje "
"resnično, je za nadaljevanje potreben način plačila. Oglejte si Metino "
"dokumentacijo o tem, `kako dodati način plačila v Meta Business Suite "
"<https://www.facebook.com/business/help/915454841921082?id=180505742745347>"
"`__."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:432
msgid ""
"`Meta Business: How to connect your phone number to your WhatsApp Business "
"account <https://www.facebook.com/business/help/456220311516626?"
"id=2129163877102343>`__"
msgstr ""
"`Meta Business: Kako povezati svojo telefonsko številko s svojim WhatsApp "
"Business računom <https://www.facebook.com/business/help/"
"456220311516626?id=2129163877102343>`__"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:434
msgid ""
"`Meta for Developers: Add a Phone Number <https://developers.facebook.com/"
"documentation/business-messaging/whatsapp/business-phone-numbers/phone-"
"numbers>`__"
msgstr ""
"`Meta for Developers: Add a Phone Number <https://developers.facebook.com/"
"documentation/business-messaging/whatsapp/business-phone-numbers/phone-"
"numbers>`__"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:440
msgid "Create a permanent token"
msgstr "Ustvari trajni žeton"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:442
msgid ""
"After configuration and testing are complete, create a permanent token to "
"replace the :guilabel:`Temporary token`."
msgstr ""
"Ko sta konfiguracija in testiranje končana, ustvarite trajni žeton, ki bo "
"zamenjal :guilabel:`Začasni žeton`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:446
msgid ""
"`Meta for Developers: System User Access Tokens <https://"
"developers.facebook.com/docs/whatsapp/business-management-api/get-"
"started#system-user- access-tokens>`__"
msgstr ""
"`Meta za razvijalce: Žetoni dostopa sistemskega uporabnika <https://"
"developers.facebook.com/docs/whatsapp/business-management-api/get-"
"started#system-user- access-tokens>`__"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:450
msgid ""
"Navigate to `Meta Business Suite <https://business.facebook.com/>`__ and "
"then go to :menuselection:`Business settings --> User --> System Users`. "
"Select an existing system user or create a new system user by "
"clicking :guilabel:`Add`."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na `Meta Business Suite <https://business.facebook.com/>`__ in nato "
"na :menuselection:`Poslovne nastavitve --> Uporabnik --> Sistemski "
"uporabniki`. Izberite obstoječega sistemskega uporabnika ali ustvarite "
"novega sistemskega uporabnika s klikom na :guilabel:`Dodaj`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:454
msgid ""
"To generate a permanent token, assets must be added to the system user. "
"Click :guilabel:`Add assets`, and a pop-up window appears. "
"Select :guilabel:`Apps` under :guilabel:`Select asset type`, then select the "
"`Odoo` app and toggle the permissions to :guilabel:`On` under "
"the :guilabel:`Full control` option, then click :guilabel:`Save Changes`. "
"Click :guilabel:`Done` in the confirmation window that appears."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje trajnega žetona morajo biti sistemskemu uporabniku dodana "
"sredstva. Kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj sredstva` in prikaže se pojavno okno. "
"Izberite :guilabel:`Aplikacije` pod :guilabel:`Izberi vrsto sredstva`, nato "
"izberite aplikacijo `Odoo` in preklopi dovoljenja na :guilabel:`Vklopljeno` "
"pod možnostjo :guilabel:`Popoln nadzor`, nato kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani "
"spremembe`. Kliknite :guilabel:`Opravljeno` v potrditvenem oknu, ki se "
"prikaže."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:460
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Generate new token`, and a pop-up window appears asking "
"which app this token should be generated for. Select the `Odoo` app, then "
"set the expiration date to either :guilabel:`60 days` or :guilabel:`Never`."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Ustvari nov žeton` in prikaže se pojavno okno, ki "
"sprašuje, za katero aplikacijo naj se ustvari ta žeton. Izberite aplikacijo "
"`Odoo`, nato nastavite datum poteka na :guilabel:`60 dni` ali "
":guilabel:`Nikoli`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:464
msgid ""
"Meta asks which permissions the system user allows. Add both of the "
"following permissions:"
msgstr ""
"Meta vpraša, katera dovoljenja sistemski uporabnik dovoljuje. Dodajte obe "
"naslednji dovoljenji:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:466
msgid "`business_management`"
msgstr "`business_management`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:467
msgid "`whatsapp_business_messaging`"
msgstr "`whatsapp_business_messaging`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:468
msgid "`whatsapp_business_management`"
msgstr "`whatsapp_business_management`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:469
msgid "`whatsapp_business_manage_events`"
msgstr "`whatsapp_business_manage_events`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:471
msgid ""
"When permissions are set, click :guilabel:`Generate token`. Copy the token "
"value that populates on the screen that follows."
msgstr ""
"Ko so dovoljenja nastavljena, kliknite :guilabel:`Ustvari žeton`. Kopirajte "
"vrednost žetona, ki se prikaže na naslednjem zaslonu."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:474
msgid ""
"With that token value, update the :guilabel:`Access Token` field in the "
"WhatsApp business account in Odoo by navigating to :menuselection:`WhatsApp "
"app --> Configuration --> WhatsApp Business Accounts`."
msgstr ""
"S to vrednostjo žetona posodobite polje :guilabel:`Žeton za dostop` v "
"poslovnem računu WhatsApp v Odoo tako, da se pomaknete na "
":menuselection:`WhatsApp aplikacija --> Konfiguracija --> Poslovni računi "
"WhatsApp`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:481
msgid "Go live with the Meta app"
msgstr "Objavi aplikacijo Meta v živo"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:483
msgid ""
"Finally, to launch the app, the Meta app must be set to :guilabel:`Live` in "
"the `Meta Developer Dashboard <https://developers.facebook.com/apps>`__. "
"Click the app that is being configured, then toggle the :guilabel:`App Mode` "
"field from :guilabel:`Development` to :guilabel:`Live`."
msgstr ""
"Nazadnje mora biti za zagon aplikacije aplikacija Meta nastavljena na "
":guilabel:`Aktivno` v `Nadzorni plošči Meta za razvijalce <https://"
"developers.facebook.com/apps>`__. Kliknite aplikacijo, ki se konfigurira, "
"nato preklopite polje :guilabel:`Način aplikacije` iz :guilabel:`Razvoj` na "
":guilabel:`Aktivno`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:488
msgid ""
"If the app status is **not** set to *live*, then the database is only able "
"to contact the test numbers specified in the developer console."
msgstr ""
"Če stanje aplikacije **ni** nastavljeno na *aktivno*, lahko zbirka podatkov "
"kontaktira samo testne številke, določene v razvijalski konzoli."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:492
msgid ""
"A privacy policy URL must be set in order for the app to be set to live. Go "
"to the `Meta Developer Dashboard <https://developers.facebook.com/apps>`__ "
"and select the `Odoo` app. Then, in the left-hand side menu, go "
"to :menuselection:`App Settings --> Basic`. Enter the privacy policy "
"hyperlink address under the :guilabel:`Privacy Policy URL` field of the "
"form. Click :guilabel:`Save changes` to apply the privacy policy to the app."
msgstr ""
"URL pravilnika o zasebnosti mora biti nastavljen, da se lahko aplikacija "
"nastavi na aktivno. Pojdite na `Nadzorno ploščo Meta za razvijalce <https://"
"developers.facebook.com/apps>`__ in izberite aplikacijo `Odoo`. Nato v "
"meniju na levi strani pojdite na :menuselection:`Nastavitve aplikacije --> "
"Osnovno`. Vnesite naslov hiperpovezave pravilnika o zasebnosti v polje "
":guilabel:`URL pravilnika o zasebnosti` obrazca. Kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani "
"spremembe`, da uporabite pravilnik o zasebnosti za aplikacijo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:498
msgid ""
"Once the app has gone live in the Meta developer console, a confirmation "
"email is sent to the administrator."
msgstr ""
"Ko je aplikacija objavljena v konzoli za razvijalce Meta, je skrbniku "
"poslano potrditveno e-poštno sporočilo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:504
msgid "WhatsApp templates"
msgstr "Predloge WhatsApp"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:506
msgid ""
"WhatsApp templates allow users to store messages that are frequently sent. "
"By creating templates tailored to specific situations, users can send pre-"
"approved messages, without having to compromise on quality or compose the "
"same text repeatedly. This ensures fast turnaround and consistent customer "
"service messaging, and increases the overall engagement rate with the "
"customer."
msgstr ""
"Predloge WhatsApp omogočajo uporabnikom shranjevanje sporočil, ki se pogosto "
"pošiljajo. Z ustvarjanjem predlog, prilagojenih določenim situacijam, lahko "
"uporabniki pošiljajo vnaprej odobrena sporočila, ne da bi morali žrtvovati "
"kakovost ali ponovno sestavljati isto besedilo. To zagotavlja hitro izvedbo "
"in dosledno sporočanje storitev za stranke ter povečuje splošno stopnjo "
"angažiranosti s stranko."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:511
msgid ""
"WhatsApp templates can be created on both the :ref:`Odoo <whatsapp/odoo-"
"templates>` and :ref:`Meta <whatsapp/meta-templates>` consoles."
msgstr ""
"Predloge WhatsApp je mogoče ustvariti tako v konzoli :ref:`Odoo <whatsapp/"
"odoo-templates>` kot v konzoli :ref:`Meta <whatsapp/meta-templates>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:515
msgid ""
"WhatsApp has an approval process that **must** be completed *before* the "
"template can be used. See :ref:`productivity/whatsapp/template-approval`."
msgstr ""
"WhatsApp ima postopek odobritve, ki se **mora** zaključiti *pred* uporabo "
"predloge. Glej :ref:`productivity/whatsapp/template-approval`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:518
msgid ""
"To access WhatsApp templates, navigate to the :menuselection:`WhatsApp app --"
"> Templates` dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Za dostop do predlog WhatsApp pojdite na nadzorno ploščo "
":menuselection:`WhatsApp aplikacija --> Predloge`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:520
msgid "Each template has three tabs:"
msgstr "Vsaka predloga ima tri zavihke:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:522
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Body`\\: stores the message body. The message body may contain "
"placeholders for dynamic content which is populated when the message is sent."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Telo`: shranjuje telo sporočila. Telo sporočila lahko vsebuje "
"označbe mesta za dinamično vsebino, ki se zapolni ob pošiljanju sporočila."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:524
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Buttons`\\: adds clickable buttons/hyperlinks at the bottom of "
"the WhatsApp template. Currently, there are three button types\\: *Quick "
"Reply*, *Visit Website*, and *Call Number*. *Visit Website* supports static, "
"dynamic, and tracked URLs."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Gumbi`: doda gumbe/hiperpovezave, na katere je mogoče klikniti, "
"na dno predloge WhatsApp. Trenutno so na voljo tri vrste gumbov: *Hiter "
"odgovor*, *Obišči spletno mesto* in *Pokliči številko*. *Obišči spletno "
"mesto* podpira statične, dinamične in sledene URL-je."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:527
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Variables`\\: lists all of the placeholders in the template, as "
"well as the variables that should be populated. For example, messages can "
"contain placeholders for a recipient's name, purchased products, or sales "
"order number."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Spremenljivke`: navaja vse označbe mest v predlogi, kot tudi "
"spremenljivke, ki jih je treba zapolniti. Sporočila lahko na primer "
"vsebujejo označbe mest za ime prejemnika, kupljene izdelke ali številko "
"prodajnega naloga."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:534
msgid "Create WhatsApp templates in Odoo"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje predlog WhatsApp v Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:536
msgid ""
"To create a WhatsApp template, go to the :menuselection:`WhatsApp app --> "
"Templates` dashboard and click :guilabel:`New`. Enter a :guilabel:`Name` for "
"the template, and select a :guilabel:`Language`."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje predloge WhatsApp pojdite na nadzorno ploščo "
":menuselection:`WhatsApp aplikacija --> Predloge` in kliknite "
":guilabel:`Novo`. Vnesite :guilabel:`Ime` predloge in izberite "
":guilabel:`Jezik`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:540
msgid ""
"In order to complete this next task, :doc:`administrator access rights <../"
"general/users/access_rights>` are needed to edit the :guilabel:`Applies to` "
"field."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:543
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Account` drop-down menu, select the *WhatsApp business "
"account* in Odoo that this template should link to. Next, under "
"the :guilabel:`Applies to` field, select the *model* the server action "
"should apply to this template."
msgstr ""
"V spustnem meniju :guilabel:`Račun` izberite *WhatsApp poslovni račun* v "
"Odoo, s katerim naj bo ta predloga povezana. Nato pod poljem "
":guilabel:`Velja za` izberite *model*, na katerega naj se strežniško dejanje "
"uporabi za to predlogo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:548
msgid ""
"These models can also be accessed in :ref:`developer mode <developer-mode>`. "
"In a contact form (or similar relevant form in Odoo), navigate to the model "
"to be referenced, and hover over a field name. This displays backend "
"information, including the specific Odoo :guilabel:`Model` name in the "
"backend. Search for the model's *frontend* name in the WhatsApp template, "
"under the :guilabel:`Applies to` drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"Do teh modelov je mogoče dostopati tudi v :ref:`razvijalskem načinu "
"<developer-mode>`. V obrazcu stika (ali podobnem ustreznem obrazcu v Odoo) "
"pojdite na model, na katerega želite sklicevati, in premaknite kazalec miške "
"nad ime polja. To prikaže zaledne informacije, vključno s specifičnim imenom "
":guilabel:`Modela` Odoo v zaledju. Poiščite *začelno* ime modela v predlogi "
"WhatsApp pod spustnim menijem :guilabel:`Velja za`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:555
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Phone Field` may produce an error when changing the model "
"or :guilabel:`Applies to` field. The :guilabel:`Phone Field` should always "
"be set to the `Phone` or `Mobile` model."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Polje telefona` lahko povzroči napako pri spreminjanju modela ali "
"polja :guilabel:`Velja za`. :guilabel:`Polje telefona` naj bo vedno "
"nastavljeno na model `Telefon` ali `Mobilni telefon`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:558
msgid ""
"To search available fields, type the frontend name in "
"the :guilabel:`Search...` box. This displays results from all of the "
"available fields for the model (:guilabel:`Applies to`) that the template is "
"created for."
msgstr ""
"Za iskanje razpoložljivih polj vnesite začelno ime v polje "
":guilabel:`Iskanje...`. To prikaže rezultate iz vseh razpoložljivih polj za "
"model (:guilabel:`Velja za`), za katerega je predloga ustvarjena."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:563
msgid ""
"To find specific fields, multiple levels may need to be navigated in the "
"search results box. Use the :icon:`fa-chevron-right` :guilabel:`(right "
"chevron)` and :icon:`fa-arrow-left` :guilabel:`(left arrow)` icons to "
"navigate between the menu levels."
msgstr ""
"Za iskanje specifičnih polj bo morda potrebno navigirati čez več ravni v "
"polju z rezultati iskanja. Uporabite ikoni :icon:`fa-chevron-right` "
":guilabel:`(puščica desno)` in :icon:`fa-arrow-left` :guilabel:`(puščica "
"levo)` za navigiranje med ravnmi menija."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:None
msgid "Searching for the phone field in the search bar."
msgstr "Iskanje polja za telefon v iskalni vrstici."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:570
msgid "Change the :guilabel:`Category` to one of the following:"
msgstr "Spremenite :guilabel:`Kategorijo` v eno izmed naslednjih:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:572
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:775
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Marketing`: Promotions or information about the business, "
"products or services. Or any message that is not utility or authentication."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Trženje`: Promocije ali informacije o podjetju, izdelkih ali "
"storitvah. Ali katerokoli sporočilo, ki ni uporabniško ali avtentikacijsko."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:574
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:777
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Utility`: Messages about a specific transaction, account, order "
"or customer request."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Uporabnost`: sporočila o določeni transakciji, računu, naročilu "
"ali zahtevi stranke."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:575
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:778
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Authentication`: One-time passwords that customers use to "
"authenticate a transaction or login."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Avtentikacija`: Enkratna gesla, ki jih stranke uporabljajo za "
"avtentikacijo transakcije ali prijave."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:579
msgid ""
"Specifying an incorrect category can cause a flag/rejected status from Meta "
"during the approval process."
msgstr ""
"Določitev napačne kategorije lahko med postopkom odobritve pri Meta povzroči "
"status označbe/zavrnitve."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:582
msgid ""
"Add any :guilabel:`Users` that are allowed to use this template. In the "
"right-side column, a :guilabel:`Header type` can be configured along with "
"a :guilabel:`Header message`, as well."
msgstr ""
"Dodajte vse :guilabel:`Uporabnike`, ki lahko uporabljajo to predlogo. V "
"desnem stolpcu je mogoče konfigurirati tudi :guilabel:`Vrsto glave` skupaj s "
":guilabel:`Sporočilom glave`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:585
msgid "The available :guilabel:`Header types` are as follows:"
msgstr "Razpoložljive :guilabel:`Vrste glav` so naslednje:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:588
msgid "Image"
msgstr "Slika"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:589
msgid "Video"
msgstr "Video"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:590
msgid "Document"
msgstr "Dokument"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:591
msgid "Location (variables need to be set)"
msgstr "Lokacija (spremenljivke je treba nastaviti)"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:593
msgid ""
"Navigate to the :guilabel:`Body` tab to configure the main message of the "
"template."
msgstr ""
"Pomaknite se na zavihek :guilabel:`Telo`, da konfigurirate glavno sporočilo "
"predloge."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:595
msgid ""
"When all the necessary changes are made to the template, click "
"the :guilabel:`Submit for approval` button in the upper-left corner, and the "
"status of the template changes to :guilabel:`Pending`."
msgstr ""
"Ko so vse potrebne spremembe predloge opravljene, kliknite gumb "
":guilabel:`Pošlji v odobritev` v zgornjem levem kotu, stanje predloge pa se "
"spremeni v :guilabel:`V teku`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:598
msgid ""
"The status remains :guilabel:`Pending` until a decision has been made by "
"Meta, whereby a confirmation email is sent indicating that the template has "
"been approved or rejected. Next, sync the templates from the Odoo database."
msgstr ""
"Stanje ostane :guilabel:`V teku`, dokler Meta ne sprejme odločitve, pri "
"čemer se pošlje potrditveno e-poštno sporočilo, ki nakazuje, da je bila "
"predloga odobrena ali zavrnjena. Nato sinhronizirajte predloge iz podatkovne "
"zbirke Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:603
msgid ":ref:`Syncing templates <productivity/whatsapp/sync-templates>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Sinhronizacija predlog <productivity/whatsapp/sync-templates>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:606
msgid ""
"Preconfigured demo data templates are available in Odoo to use or modify. "
"These templates can be used as-is or modified to suit a specific business "
"need."
msgstr ""
"V Odoo so na voljo vnaprej konfigurirane predloge demonstracijskih podatkov "
"za uporabo ali prilagajanje. Te predloge lahko uporabite kot so ali jih "
"prilagodite glede na specifične poslovne potrebe."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:609
msgid ""
"To use these templates, navigate to :menuselection:`WhatsApp app --> "
"Templates` and select a preconfigured template. Click :guilabel:`Submit for "
"Approval` to start the approval process. An email is sent to the "
"administrator of the Meta account when the template has been approved."
msgstr ""
"Za uporabo teh predlog pojdite na :menuselection:`Aplikacija WhatsApp --> "
"Predloge` in izberite vnaprej konfigurirano predlogo. Kliknite "
":guilabel:`Pošlji v odobritev`, da začnete postopek odobritve. Ko je "
"predloga odobrena, je administratorju Meta računa poslan e-poštni naslov."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:616
msgid "Buttons"
msgstr "Gumbi"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:618
msgid ""
"Buttons can be added into the message from the :guilabel:`Buttons` tab. "
"Enter the :guilabel:`Type` (either :guilabel:`Visit "
"Website`, :guilabel:`Call Number`, or :guilabel:`Quick Reply`), and then "
"specify the :guilabel:`Button Text`, :guilabel:`Call Number` "
"or :guilabel:`Website URL` (including :guilabel:`Url Type`), depending on "
"the :guilabel:`Type` of button."
msgstr ""
"V sporočilo je mogoče dodati gumbe iz zavihka :guilabel:`Gumbi`. Vnesite "
":guilabel:`Vrsto` (bodisi :guilabel:`Obiščite spletno mesto`, "
":guilabel:`Pokliči številko` ali :guilabel:`Hitri odgovor`) in nato določite "
":guilabel:`Besedilo gumba`, :guilabel:`Telefonska številka` ali "
":guilabel:`URL spletnega mesta` (vključno z :guilabel:`Vrsto URL-ja`), "
"odvisno od :guilabel:`Vrste` gumba."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:624
msgid ""
"Buttons can also be added on the `Meta Business Suite <https://"
"business.facebook.com/wa/manage/home>`__. To see Meta's WhatsApp template "
"dashboard, go to :menuselection:`Account tools --> Message templates`."
msgstr ""
"Gumbe je mogoče dodati tudi v `Meta Business Suite <https://"
"business.facebook.com/wa/manage/home>`__. Za ogled nadzorne plošče predlog "
"WhatsApp v Meta pojdite na :menuselection:`Orodja računa --> Predloge "
"sporočil`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:631
msgid "Placeholders and variables"
msgstr "Označbe mest in spremenljivke"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:633
msgid ""
"Dynamic variables reference certain fields within the Odoo database to "
"produce unique data in the WhatsApp message when using a template. Dynamic "
"variables are encoded to display fields from within the database, "
"referencing fields from within a model."
msgstr ""
"Dinamične spremenljivke se sklicujejo na določena polja v zbirki podatkov "
"Odoo, da ustvarijo edinstvene podatke v sporočilu WhatsApp pri uporabi "
"predloge. Dinamične spremenljivke so kodirane za prikaz polj iz zbirke "
"podatkov in se sklicujejo na polja v modelu."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:638
msgid ""
"Many companies like to customize their WhatsApp messages with a personalized "
"piece of customer information to grab attention. This can be accomplished in "
"Odoo by referencing a field within a model by setting a dynamic variable. "
"For example, a customer's name can be referenced in the email from "
"the :guilabel:`Customer` field on the :guilabel:`Sales Order` model."
msgstr ""
"Številna podjetja rada prilagodijo sporočila WhatsApp z osebnim delom "
"informacij o stranki, da pritegnejo pozornost. To je mogoče doseči v Odoo s "
"sklicevanjem na polje v modelu z nastavitvijo dinamične spremenljivke. Na "
"primer, ime stranke je mogoče navesti v e-pošti iz polja :guilabel:`Stranka` "
"v modelu :guilabel:`Prodajni nalog`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:None
msgid "WhatsApp message with dynamic variables highlighted."
msgstr "Sporočilo WhatsApp s poudarjenimi dinamičnimi spremenljivkami."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:646
msgid ""
"Dynamic variables can be added in to the :guilabel:`Body` by "
"adding :guilabel:`placeholders` in the *text*. To add a placeholder in the "
"*message body* enter the following text `{{1}}`. For the second placeholder "
"enter `{{2}}` and increase incrementally as more placeholders are added to "
"the text."
msgstr ""
"Dinamične spremenljivke je mogoče dodati v :guilabel:`Telo` z dodajanjem "
":guilabel:`ogradnih mest` v *besedilo*. Če želite dodati ogradno mesto v "
"*telo sporočila*, vnesite naslednje besedilo `{{1}}`. Za drugo ogradno mesto "
"vnesite `{{2}}` in povečujte postopoma, ko dodajate več ogradnih mest v "
"besedilo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:651
msgid "*The following is the text from payment receipt template body:*"
msgstr "*Naslednje je besedilo iz telesa predloge potrdila o plačilu:*"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:653
msgid "Dear {{1}},"
msgstr "Spoštovani {{1}},"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:0
msgid "Here is your invoice *{{2}}* from *{{3}}* for a total of *{{4}}{{5}}*."
msgstr "Tukaj je vaš račun *{{2}}* od *{{3}}* za skupni znesek *{{4}}{{5}}*."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:0
msgid "To review your invoice or pay online: {{6}}"
msgstr "Za pregled računa ali plačilo prek spleta: {{6}}"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:658
msgid "Thank you"
msgstr "Hvala"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:661
msgid ":ref:`productivity/whatsapp/templates`"
msgstr ":ref:`productivity/whatsapp/templates`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:663
msgid ""
"These placeholders **must** be configured on the :guilabel:`Variables` tab "
"of the template before submitting for approval from Meta. To edit the "
"dynamic variables on a template, first change the :guilabel:`Type` "
"to :guilabel:`Field of Model`. This allows Odoo to reference a field within "
"a model to produce unique data in the message being sent."
msgstr ""
"Te označbe mest **morajo** biti konfigurirane na zavihku "
":guilabel:`Spremenljivke` predloge pred pošiljanjem v odobritev Meta. Za "
"urejanje dinamičnih spremenljivk v predlogi najprej spremenite "
":guilabel:`Vrsto` v :guilabel:`Polje modela`. To omogoča Odoo, da se "
"sklicuje na polje znotraj modela in ustvari edinstvene podatke v sporočilu, "
"ki se pošilja."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:668
msgid ""
"Next, edit the :guilabel:`Field` of the dynamic variables. "
"The :guilabel:`Applies to` field in the template should be edited prior to "
"ensure the correct model and field are referenced."
msgstr ""
"Nato uredite :guilabel:`Polje` dinamičnih spremenljivk. Polje "
":guilabel:`Velja za` v predlogi je treba urediti vnaprej, da se zagotovi "
"sklicevanje na pravilni model in polje."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:671
msgid ""
"To search the available fields, type in the front-end name of the field in "
"the search box. This finds a result from all of the available fields for the "
"model (:guilabel:`Applies to`) that the template is created for. There may "
"be multiple levels that need to be configured."
msgstr ""
"Za iskanje razpoložljivih polj vnesite uporabniško ime polja v iskalno "
"polje. To najde rezultat izmed vseh razpoložljivih polj za model "
"(:guilabel:`Velja za`), za katerega je predloga ustvarjena. Morda bo treba "
"konfigurirati več ravni."

